{"lemma":"جَنّاتٌ","slug":"جَنّاتٌ","root":"ج.ن.ن","root_slug":"ج-ن-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ن-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَنَّة","root":"جنن","pos":"N","occurrence_count":147},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6376","n6380","n6381","n6382"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"garden"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"paradise, heaven, the Paradise, the Heaven, Elysium"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جُنَّ (junna)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"madness, craziness, possession, mania"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a jinn, demon, genie","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"jinn, demons, genies","tags":["Classical","plural","plural-only"],"examples":[{"text":"مِنَ ٱلْجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","english":"from among the jinn/demons and Men."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thing which veils, conceals, hides, covers, or protects"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"weapon or armor, a thing used to protect oneself, anything protective or defensive"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"piece of cloth which a woman wears covering the face and the two sides of the bosom, a type of hijab or veil"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Inherited from Proto-Semitic, the sense of a paradise being borrowed from Classical Syriac ܓܰܢܬܳܐ (gannəṯā). Compare Hebrew גַּן (gan), Aramaic גִּנָּא (ginnā), Ugaritic 𐎂𐎐 (gn). Synchronically, related to جَنّ (jann, “covering, protecting”)"},"ipa":["/d͡ʒan.na/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6376","headword_ar":"جَنَّهُ","root":"jn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~N","text_ar":"جَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It veiled, concealed, hid, covered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protected, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K;) said of the night; (S, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~a Ealayohi","text_ar":"جَنَّ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnN","text_ar":"جُنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~N","text_ar":"جَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or both; (TA;) so in the Kur vi. 76, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it veiled him, concealed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covered him, with its darkness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajn~hu","text_ar":"اجنّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb, K:) or this last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gave him, that which should veil him, conceal him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. : accord. to Er-Rághib, the primary signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~N","text_ar":"جَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"veiling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the sense."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~a Eanohu","text_ar":"جُنَّ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(anything)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was veiled, concealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hidden, from him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He concealed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a dead body; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajn~hu","text_ar":"اجنّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) or the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wrapped it in grave-clothing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he buried it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aYo'a fiY SadoriY","text_ar":"الشَّىْءَ فِى صَدْرِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajonanotu","text_ar":"اَجْنَنْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I concealed the thing in my bosom."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waladFA","text_ar":"وَلَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajan~ato","text_ar":"اَجَنَّتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janiynFA","text_ar":"جَنِينًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) said of a woman, (S,) or a pregnant female, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She concealed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enveloped"},{"kind":"text","text":"in her womb"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an embryo,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fœtus"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~a","text_ar":"جَنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~N","text_ar":"جِنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an embryo, or a fœtus,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was concealed"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the womb. (K.) ―         -b2-  Also, [inf. n., probably,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~N","text_ar":"جِنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnN","text_ar":"جُنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janaAnN","text_ar":"جَنَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained below,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the night)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dark."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Golius on the authority of Ibn-Maaroof.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~a","text_ar":"جُنَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnN","text_ar":"جُنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~apN","text_ar":"جِنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~N","text_ar":"جَنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ausotujin~N","text_ar":"اُسْتُجِنٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tjn~n","text_ar":"تجنّن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tjAn~","text_ar":"تجانّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majonuwn","text_ar":"مَجْنُون"},{"kind":"text","text":"[originally signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessed by a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~iY~","text_ar":"جِنِّىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~","text_ar":"جِنّ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessed by a devil"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see Bd li. 39;) and hence meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bereft of reason;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mad, insane, unsound in mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intellect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wanting therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the verbs may generally be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, possessed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"insane"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~a Al*~ubaAbu","text_ar":"جُنَّ الذُّبَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnN","text_ar":"جُنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The flies made much buzzing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made a gladsome buzzing"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a meadow. (A, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~a Aln~abotu","text_ar":"جُنَّ النَّبْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnN","text_ar":"جُنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The herbage became tall, and tangled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"luxuriant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant and dense, and put forth its flowers"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blossoms:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became thick and tall and full-grown, and blossomed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~ati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"جُنَّتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnN","text_ar":"جُنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The land produced pleasing herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plants:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put forth its flowers and blossoms;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tjn~nt","text_ar":"تجنّنت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","TA","Msb","A","Fr"]},{"entry_id":"n6380","headword_ar":"جَنَّةٌ","root":"jn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garden, such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"busotaAn","text_ar":"بُسْتَان"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walled garden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hadiyqap","text_ar":"حَدِيقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palm-trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palms and other trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"if containing palm-trees and grape-vines;"},{"kind":"text","text":"otherwise, if containing trees, called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hdyqp","text_ar":"حديقة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Aboo-'Alee in the Tedhkireh, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bstAn","text_ar":"بستان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having trees by which the ground is concealed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealing trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tall palm-trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shadowing trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the tangling, or luxuriousness of their branches; as though concealing at once what is beneath them: then"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bstAn","text_ar":"بستان"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because of its dense and shadowing trees: (Bd in ii. 23:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bstAn","text_ar":"بستان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of palms and other trees, dense, and shadowing by the tangling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"luxuriousness, and denseness, of their branches;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were originally the inf. n. of un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~ahu","text_ar":"جَنَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and meaning “ a single act of veiling ” or “ concealing ” &c.: (Ksh ib.:) then, with the article"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Paradise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the abode of recompense;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinaAn","text_ar":"جِنَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"therein; (Ksh and Bd ib.;) or because the various delights prepared therein for mankind are concealed in the present state of existence: (Bd ib.:) [and] hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aljan~aAtu","text_ar":"الجَنَّاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the gardens"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Paradise], (so in a copy of the S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~aAtu EadonK","text_ar":"جَنَّاتُ عَدْنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the gardens of continual abode"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (so in another copy of the S:) [for] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jan~apN","text_ar":"جَنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajin~apN","text_ar":"اَجِنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinayonap","text_ar":"جِنَيْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jun~apN","text_ar":"جُنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this last is strange. (MF, TA.) [Dim. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junayonapN","text_ar":"جُنَيْنَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", vulgarly pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jinayonap","text_ar":"جِنَيْنَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A garden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a little Paradise."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6381","headword_ar":"جُنَّةٌ","root":"jn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing by which a person is veiled, concealed, hidden, covered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protected: an arm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"armour, with which one protects himself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything protective:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coats of mail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any defensive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protective, arm"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"armour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junanN","text_ar":"جُنَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of cloth which a woman wears, covering the fore and kind parts of her head, but not the middle of it, and covering the face, and the two sides of the bosom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or, accord. to the M,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the ornaments"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuliY~","text_ar":"حُلِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"janobaY","text_ar":"جَنْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the bosom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and having two eyeholes, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroquE","text_ar":"بُرْقُع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6382","headword_ar":"جِنَّةٌ","root":"jn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see its syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jin~N","text_ar":"جِنٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":":       -A2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"junuwnN","text_ar":"جُنُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}